# Favicon environment tint. The showcase favicon hue-shifts per environment so
# multiple running instances are easy to tell apart (dev/staging/prod tabs, or
# several dev servers at once). Valid values: dev | staging | prod.
#
# You usually don't need to set this: `astro dev` auto-selects "dev" and a build
# defaults to "prod" (the untouched aurora). Set it to "staging" on your staging
# deploy — as a real CI/host env var, or by copying this file to `.env`.
# PUBLIC_APP_ENV=staging
